{
  "stem": "5313.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You know, it was a, if I recall, is an army camp must have been before.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they made a hospital out of it where they put us sick people over there.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "That was near Sachsenhausen?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Near Sachsenhausen, yes.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Recall the day what happened but I don't recall exactly--",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--date was.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was there for about a week or 10 days until I got really a little bit stronger.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they needed the space, you know, for more sick people than I was.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So they just give us food and they asked where we want to go.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I happened to line up to go to Bergen-Belsen.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I didn't even know how did I get there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I happened to arrive to Bergen-Belsen, which that was already in an English zone.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] but would say a week or 10 days later, I become the police chief of the camp.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They needed some stronger people who speak the language.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I become the police chief.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And one of my friend, you know, who I met him here in United State and we was friends for many years, which we still are, he was head of the food distribution.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So Bergen-Belsen become-- it was a very big camp and it was well known, you know, how many people really perished there and how many died in that particular camp.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But that was very interesting work for me that I had a chance, you know, to some of my little way to pay back for the German that I went I started to hunt with my friends, you know.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And what we did, you know, we worked over a few of them and then we turned it over to the English authorities.",
      "word_count": 23
    }
  ],
